  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Frigates are fast and maneuverable military ships. They=
 are
  typically the most numerous type of military ship for an empire.<o:p></o:=
p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>You should build lots of frigates to patrol outlying mi=
ning
  stations and to escort construction ships.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>With their high speed and potent armament, frigates are
  particularly well-suited to defending against raiding pirates</span>.<span
